celopg.answers.funding_sources: Ecofrontiers is a privately-run, two-person agency and is a SARL based in Provence, France. It has no investors and its revenues come from service-based work for clients in the climate and crypto sectors. Learn more at https://ecofrontiers.xyz/  Previously, prior to the spinout of the Regen Atlas, Ecofrontiers received $1576.30 in grant funding for developing the Regen Atlas’ initial prototype (see Gitcoin checker: https://checker.gitcoin.co/public/project/show/ecofrontiers-crypto-natural-capital-aggregator). This is the only grant funding to date Ecofrontiers has collected to date for its work.
